接口 Binary

  • 所有超级接口:
    Cancelable
    所有已知实现类:
    BasicBinary, BitmapBinary, ByteArrayBinary, FileBinary, InputStreamBinary

    public interface Binary
extends Cancelable

    File interface. All the methods are called in Son thread.

    Created in Oct 12, 2015 4:44:07 PM.
    作者:
    Yan Zhenjie.

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      String getFileName()
      Return the fileName, Can be null.
      long getLength()
      Returns the size of the Binary, if size is 0, the Binary Field will not be sent.
      String getMimeType()
      Return mimeType of binary.
      void onWriteBinary(OutputStream outputStream)
      Write your Binary data through flow out.

      • 从接口继承的方法 com.yolanda.nohttp.able.Cancelable

        cancel, isCanceled

    • 方法详细资料

      • getLength

        long getLength()
        Returns the size of the Binary, if size is 0, the Binary Field will not be sent. The rest of the Binary method will not be invoked.
        返回:
        Long length.

      • onWriteBinary

        void onWriteBinary(OutputStream outputStream)
        Write your Binary data through flow out.
        参数:
        outputStream - OutputStream.

      • getFileName

        String getFileName()
        Return the fileName, Can be null.
        返回:
        File name.

      • getMimeType

        String getMimeType()
        Return mimeType of binary.
        返回:
        MimeType.
